    "• Sensor Noise: Real-time sensor data can be affected by noise and environmental variability, impacting the EKG's ability to validate task plans.",
    "Future Directions • Enhance Knowledge Graph Coverage: Integrate comprehensive datasets and real-time updates to expand the EKG's scope.",
